spanGrp.span: Arungral hale ajung ṭum nu̠, kalenbung ki hale ruwngkhu dọnu̠ amha le epāl vaje
Came from Arungral and sattle at Kalengbung, Rungkhu
le jāngkel loon hale pāl jenu̠
Anār khullen hale ama vatun va
to Anāl khullen and he establised the village
angnal, angnal hmiing to pahor nu̠
when it was called as angnāl, now the Anāl
hmiing to angnal hmiing vahol hloh va
the Anāl name has carried the name of Angnāl
pakan ruwngkhu tuwng va amjā varen de
khu to vavang tung ki, angnar khu angnar khu dọte
established the village and when it was called as Angnal village
nani hin angnal hmiing to nahol hloh vahin
